data.description: Welcome to your new home! You do not want to miss out on the large backyard that this home offers. Inside you'll find the perfect layout with an open floor plan of a dining area, kitchen and living room. In the dining area you'll find built ins, perfect for you to really customize your living area and add a little character to your home. This home also comes equipped with a brand new water heater and sprinkler system. This affordable, well maintained and one owner home is just waiting for you. Come see it now!
